    "As Fig. 15 SlowFast Model.",
    "(Feichtenhofer et al. 2019) shown in Fig. 15, the two paths are the low frame rate and the high frame rate.",
    "T and C of the slow path are the benchmarks of the fast path.",
    "For video, the slow path samples T frames as the input.",
    "At the same time, the fast path needs to process high-frequency information; the whole process does not use the time domain downsampling layer, so the input is always -framed."
